    • Uses of ApplicationType in com.sun.tools.visualvm.application

      Methods in com.sun.tools.visualvm.application with parameters of type ApplicationType 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      protected static String ApplicationDescriptor.resolveApplicationName(Application application, ApplicationType type)
      Returns Application name if available in Snapshot Storage as PROPERTY_NAME or user-provided display name defined by JVM argument -Dvisualvm.display.name (since VisualVM 1.3.4) or generates new name using the provided ApplicationType.
